quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,When earth dur quaked
  99,2,earth ejects its sarcina
  99,3,Uman vointa uimire Ce exista întîmplare
  99,4,Ala zi el exprima its stire
  99,5,Ala vostri Domnitor comanda el
  99,6,Ala zi popor decurge every direcie arata their munca
  99,7,Oricine does atom greutate bun vointa vedea el
  99,8,Oricine does atom greutate evil vointa vedea el